The paper deals with fairness in machine learning, specifically in the context of principal component analysis (PCA) and kernel PCA. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
